name: AztecEncodeOptions
summary: Options for future Aztec encoding support.

properties.name: Layers
properties.summary: Target number of layers. When null, the encoder will choose automatically.

properties.name: ErrorCorrectionPercent
properties.summary: Target error correction percentage. When null, the encoder will choose automatically.

properties.name: Compact
properties.summary: When true, encode as compact Aztec when possible.
